1. Mi smo *pobedili* našeg protivnika u finalnoj utakmici. (We *won* against our opponent in the final match.)
2. Oni su *pobedili* na izborima. (They *won* the elections.)
3. Ja ne bih *pobedio* u trci da nisam trenirao. (I wouldn't have *won* the race if I hadn't trained.)
4. Da li si čuo da su naši košarkaši *pobedili* Amerikance? (Did you hear that our basketball players *defeated* the Americans?)
5. Kada smo *pobedili*, proslavili smo sa tortom i šampanjcem. (When we *won*, we celebrated with cake and champagne.)
6. Bez obzira koliko se trudili, nikada nećete *pobediti* protiv prirode. (No matter how hard you try, you will never *defeat* nature.)
7. Ove godine smo *pobedili* na međunarodnom takmičenju u matematici. (This year we *won* at the international math competition.)
8. Kada smo *pobedili* u igri, drugi su bili ljubomorni. (When we *won* the game, others were jealous.)